# HTML & CSS Conventions

## ⚠️ CRITICAL: Design System Preservation

**NEVER CHANGE** the existing design system unless explicitly requested by the user. All new components must match the current styling exactly.

## Color System

**MUST PRESERVE** these color variables - DO NOT CHANGE without explicit user permission:

```css
/* Background Colors */
--bg-primary: #1a1a1a    /* Main background */
--bg-secondary: #2a2a2a  /* Cards/sidebar */
--bg-tertiary: #3a3a3a   /* Hover/active */

/* Text Colors */
--text-primary: #fff     /* Headings */
--text-secondary: #e1e1e1 /* Regular text */
--text-muted: #b1b1b1    /* Secondary text */
--text-disabled: #7a7a7a /* Disabled text */

/* Accent Colors */
--accent-primary: #4a9eff  /* Primary buttons */
--accent-warning: #ff9800  /* Filter displays */
--accent-success: #5a9eff  /* Selected states */
```

